ðŸ“Š API Endpoints Reference
Authentication
Method    Endpoint           Access    Description 
POST     /api/auth/register  Public    Register new user
POST     /api/auth/login     Public    Login user
GET      /api/auth/me        Protected Get current user
PUT      /api/auth/profile   Protected Update profile

Users
Method     Endpoint           Access        Description
GET        /api/users         Admin         Get all users
GET        /api/users/:id     Protected     Get user by ID
PUT        /api/users/:id     Admin/HR      Update user
DELETE     /api/users/:id     Admin         Delete user

Attendance
Method      Endpoint                        Access          Description
POST        /api/attendance                ProtectedMark   attendance
GET         /api/attendance/my-attendance  Protected       Get my attendance
GET         /api/attendance/all            Admin/HR        Get all attendance

Leaves
Method           Endpoint                 Access               Description
POST            /api/leaves/apply         Protected            Apply for leave
GET            /api/leaves/my-leaves      Protected            Get my leaves
GET            /api/leaves/pending        Approvers            Get pending leaves
PUT            /api/leaves/:id/status     Approvers            Approve/reject leave
POST           /api/leaves/allocate       Admin/HR             Allocate leaves

Payroll
Method         Endpoint                          Access                Description
POST           /api/payroll/payrun               Payroll/Admin         Create payrun
POST           /api/payroll/payrun/:id/process   Payroll/Admin         Process payrun
GET            /api/payroll/payruns              Payroll/Admin         Get all payruns
GET            /api/payroll/payrun/:id/payslips  Payroll/Admin         Get payslips
GET            /api/payroll/my-payslips          Protected             Get my payslips
GET            /api/payroll/payslip/:id/download Protected             Download payslip PDF

Dashboard
Method         Endpoint                Access                 Description
GET            /api/dashboard/admin    Admin                  Get admin dashboard
GET            /api/dashboard/employee Protected              Get employee dashboard

